{
	"circus_minigame": {
		"repeatable": true,
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "if",
				"condition": {
					"event_unused": "circus_clown_intro"
				},
				"then": [
					{
						"type": "mark_used",
						"event": "circus_clown_intro"
					},
					{
						"type": "set_var",
						"vars": {
							"circus_minigame_fee": {
								"set": 10
							}
						}
					},
					{
						"type": "set_var",
						"vars": {
							"circus_strength_wins": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_strength_losses": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_strength_played": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_skill_wins": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_skill_losses": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_skill_played": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_wit_wins": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_wit_losses": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_wit_played": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_luck_wins": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_luck_losses": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_luck_played": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_minigame_wins": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_minigame_losses": {
								"set": 0
							},
							"circus_minigame_played": {
								"set": 0
							}
						}
					},
					{
						"type": "text",
						"text": "\"Step right up, step right up!\"\n\nPerched atop a garish red-and-purple booth, a short figure in a porcelain mask — one half grinning, the other frowning — throws their arms wide as you approach.\n\n\"You. Yes, you. You've got the look of someone who to wants to have some fun!\"",
						"clear": true,
						"no_continue": true
					},
					{
						"type": "text",
						"text": "They vault off the booth and land in a crouch that shouldn't quite work, then straighten up, with too much energy.\n\n\"Welcome — welcome — to the Games of the Gilded Hollow.\" They spread their arms wide. \"Games of strength! Games of skill! Games of wit and luck and more!\"\n\n\"Play the games! Seek victory! And who knows — maybe you'll walk away with something Fabulous!\" [font_size=-2]\"Nobody ever has. But I do like to say it.\"[/font_size]",
						"clear": false,
						"no_continue": true
					}
				],
				"else": [
					{
						"type": "random",
						"outcomes": [
							{
								"weight": 1,
								"steps": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "\"Back again.\" They spot you before you're halfway to the booth. \"Of course you are. They always come back.\"",
										"clear": true,
										"no_continue": true
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"weight": 1,
								"steps": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "They see you coming from across the grounds. The mask tilts sideways.\n\n\"Oh, it's you.\" A pause. \"Feeling lucky today? Or just feeling generous?\"",
										"clear": true,
										"no_continue": true
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"weight": 1,
								"steps": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "\"Back for more, are we?\" The clown claps twice, sharply, and drops into a bow. \"Splendid. Truly.\"",
										"clear": true,
										"no_continue": true
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"weight": 1,
								"steps": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "The mask turns toward you before you've said a word.\n\n\"You again.\" They clap once. \"Good, good! I was starting to get bored.\"",
										"clear": true,
										"no_continue": true
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"weight": 1,
								"steps": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "\"Ah!\" They point as you approach. \"My favorite — no, I say that to everyone.\" They lower the finger. \"But you. You're actually starting to grow on me. Or maybe not. Who knows?\"",
										"clear": true,
										"no_continue": true
									}
								]
							}
						]
					}
				]
			},
			{
				"type": "event",
				"event": "circus_minigame_choices"
			}
		]
	},
	"circus_minigame_back": {
		"repeatable": true,
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "random",
				"outcomes": [
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "\"No?\" They look at the empty counter. \"Fine. You know where I am when you change your mind.\"",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": false
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "\"Tch.\" They turn away and start rearranging dice. \"Come back when you're feeling generous.\"",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": false
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "They stare at you. Then wave a hand. \"Go. Go on. Come back richer.\"",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": false
							}
						]
					}
				]
			},
			{
				"type": "event",
				"event": "circus_minigame_choices"
			}
		]
	},
	"circus_minigame_choices": {
		"repeatable": true,
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "random",
				"outcomes": [
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "The calliope grinds through a half-familiar melody somewhere deeper in the grounds.",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "A cheer rises from further in the circus. Then it stops, cleanly.",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "One of the harlequins drifts past behind the booth, white mask blank, not looking at you.",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "The smell of fried oil and sawdust hangs heavy around the stand.",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "From somewhere behind the tent, something shifts in its cage and then goes still.",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					}
				]
			},
			{
				"type": "random",
				"outcomes": [
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "\"So.\" They point at you. \"What'll it be?\"",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "They lean on the counter and tap it twice. \"What'll it be?\"",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "\"Don't be shy.\" They wave a hand. \"Pick your poison.\"",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "They stare. The mask grins. And frowns. \"Well?\"",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "\"Take your time.\" They drum their fingers on the counter. \"I'm not going anywhere. Neither are you, really.\"",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					}
				]
			},
			{
				"type": "choice",
				"header": "What would you like to do?",
				"choices": [
					{
						"choice": "Ask about prizes",
						"key": "prizes"
					},
					{
						"choice": "Ask about current wins",
						"key": "wins"
					},
					{
						"choice": "Play a Game",
						"key": "play"
					},
					{
						"choice": "Leave",
						"key": "back",
						"type": "back"
					}
				],
				"branches": {
					"prizes": [
						{
							"type": "event",
							"event": "circus_reward_list"
						}
					],
					"wins": [
						{
							"type": "event",
							"event": "circus_minigame_score"
						}
					],
					"play": [
						{
							"type": "event",
							"event": "circus_minigame_games"
						}
					]
				}
			}
		]
	},
